before). Also, since it is a PvP server, you can farm the PLAYERS that are farming plat (although you may wanna wait till you're higher lvl than most there, heh). South Karana has the Treants, that should still be good for you with fairly decent loot. For straight exp, you can't go wrong with OT. It is almost exclusively dark, and while the loot sucks, the exp in a good group should own. Lastly, you should know that you play one of the ultimate farming classes. I never really made money with my mage on TZ till I was like lvl 50, and then I would just go farm items, or plat off HG's at my liesure. For spells, and yeah, I know this is a little lame, but hunting wisps, and doing the concordance of research quest nets you approx 10pp for each book you sell back. That should be no problem, just tedious maybe. Well, that was a LOT longer than I intended, and if you read it all, I hope it helps. Send Laidee a tell sometime if you see me on I have bought many a mage thier spells, or researched them. I'd be glad to help you out if I can <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  . <p>Laidee Lightbane &lt;BR&gt;<br>
